# Gateway service — environment template
#
# The gateway currently serves mock dashboard/learn/upcoming data with no
# environment variables. This file exists for consistency with other services.
#
# Docker Compose loads the repo-root .env (see ../../.env.example) but the
# gateway does not read any variables from it today.
#
# If you add configuration later (auth, upstream LMS URLs, feature flags),
# document variables here and in the root .env.example.
